title: Hi there!
par1: My name is Aleksandra and I have many years of experience as a professional cleaner. I have been working together with my team for
par2: years here in Stockholm. We offer all types of cleaning. We have a partnership with the insurance company Trygg-Hansa. This means that we offers compensation for events that caused damage when we performed our work at the customer's place or if keys were to go missing.
